{
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "uid": "contextcore-tasks",
  "title": "Project Tasks",
  "description": "View project tasks as OpenTelemetry spans from Tempo. Core ContextCore dashboard for task tracking and workflow history.",
  "tags": [
    "contextcore",
    "core",
    "tasks"
  ],
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-7d",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "",
  "version": 1,
  "weekStart": "",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "project",
        "label": "Project",
        "type": "custom",
        "current": {
          "text": "beaver-lead-contractor",
          "value": "beaver-lead-contractor"
        },
        "options": [
          {
            "text": "beaver-lead-contractor",
            "value": "beaver-lead-contractor",
            "selected": true
          },
          {
            "text": "dashboard-persistence",
            "value": "dashboard-persistence"
          },
          {
            "text": "ajidamoo-squirrel",
            "value": "ajidamoo-squirrel"
          },
          {
            "text": "asabikeshiinh-localization",
            "value": "asabikeshiinh-localization"
          },
          {
            "text": "contextcore-tui-fixes",
            "value": "contextcore-tui-fixes"
          },
          {
            "text": "demo-project",
            "value": "demo-project"
          },
          {
            "text": "contextcore",
            "value": "contextcore"
          }
        ],
        "query": "beaver-lead-contractor,dashboard-persistence,ajidamoo-squirrel,asabikeshiinh-localization,contextcore-tui-fixes,demo-project,contextcore"
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Project Overview",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 100,
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Projects with Activity",
      "type": "table",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "tempo",
        "uid": "tempo"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": {
              "type": "auto"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "showHeader": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "tempo",
            "uid": "tempo"
          },
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "query": "{resource.project.id != \"\"} | select(resource.project.id)",
          "limit": 100,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Tasks - ${project}",
      "type": "table",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 1
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "tempo",
        "uid": "tempo"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": {
              "type": "auto"
            }
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "task.status"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background",
                  "mode": "basic"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "mappings",
                "value": [
                  {
                    "type": "value",
                    "options": {
                      "pending": {
                        "color": "yellow",
                        "text": "PENDING"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "value",
                    "options": {
                      "in_progress": {
                        "color": "blue",
                        "text": "IN PROGRESS"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "value",
                    "options": {
                      "done": {
                        "color": "green",
                        "text": "DONE"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "value",
                    "options": {
                      "blocked": {
                        "color": "red",
                        "text": "BLOCKED"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "showHeader": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "tempo",
            "uid": "tempo"
          },
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "query": "{resource.project.id = \"$project\"} | select(span.task.id, span.task.title, span.task.status, span.task.type)",
          "limit": 50,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Workflow Runs",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9
      },
      "id": 101,
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Workflow Executions",
      "type": "table",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 10
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "tempo",
        "uid": "tempo"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": {
              "type": "auto"
            }
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "workflow.status"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background",
                  "mode": "basic"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "mappings",
                "value": [
                  {
                    "type": "value",
                    "options": {
                      "running": {
                        "color": "blue",
                        "text": "RUNNING"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "value",
                    "options": {
                      "completed": {
                        "color": "green",
                        "text": "COMPLETED"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "value",
                    "options": {
                      "failed": {
                        "color": "red",
                        "text": "FAILED"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Duration"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "ms"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "showHeader": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "tempo",
            "uid": "tempo"
          },
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "query": "{name =~ \"workflow.*\"} | select(resource.project.id, span.workflow.id, span.workflow.status, span.workflow.type, duration)",
          "limit": 50,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Workflow Trigger",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 18
      },
      "id": 102,
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "title": "Trigger Workflow - ${project}",
      "type": "contextcore-workflow-panel",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 19
      },
      "options": {
        "apiUrl": "http://localhost:8082",
        "projectId": "$project",
        "showDryRun": true,
        "showExecute": true,
        "confirmExecution": true,
        "refreshInterval": 10
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "title": "CLI Commands (Fallback)",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 19
      },
      "options": {
        "content": "### Run Workflows via CLI\n\nIf the workflow panel is not available, use the CLI:\n\n```bash\n# Dry run (preview without executing)\ncontextcore workflow run --project ${project} --dry-run\n\n# Execute workflow\ncontextcore workflow run --project ${project}\n\n# Check workflow status\ncontextcore workflow status --id <workflow-id>\n```\n\n### Plugin Installation\n\nTo enable the workflow trigger panel:\n\n```bash\ncd contextcore-owl\nnpm install && npm run build\ndocker compose restart grafana\n```",
        "mode": "markdown"
      }
    }
  ]
}